21#define SSH_PKCS11_ERR_LOGIN_FAIL 2
22#define SSH_PKCS11_ERR_NO_SLOTS 3
23#define SSH_PKCS11_ERR_PIN_REQUIRED 4
24#define SSH_PKCS11_ERR_PIN_LOCKED 5
